tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE course (course_id INT PRIMARY KEY, course_name TEXT, instructor TEXT, start_date DATE, end_date DATE)
CREATE TABLE student (student_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_name TEXT, email TEXT, enrollment_date DATE, graduation_date DATE)
CREATE TABLE enrollment (enrollment_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, enrollment_date DATE)
CREATE TABLE completion (completion_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, course_id INT, completion_date DATE)
CREATE TABLE engagement (engagement_id INT PRIMARY KEY, student_id INT, engagement_date DATE, interaction_type TEXT)
